text: Mariana Sahakian (born September 2, 1977) is a Lebanese table tennis player. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's singles event, in which she was eliminated in the preliminary round by Nigerian Olufunke Oshonaike. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Lebanese female table tennis players Category:Olympic table tennis players of Lebanon Category:Table tennis players at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Table tennis players at the 2006 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for Lebanon
